supervisor.model

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • supervisor.model.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
    The main model of the Supervisor in the model-view-controller. Contains the status of the machines, and of the election in general. Manages nearly all administrative functions of the election, including accepting machines onto the network, generating and traking voters and pins, authorizing machines, opening and closing elections, and much more. Also contains a link to Auditorium, for broadcasting (and hearing) messages on the network.
